FOOL O madam, yonder is heavy news within, between two soldiers and my young lady. 

COUNTESS What is the matter?	 

FOOL Nay, there is some comfort in the news, some comfort. Your son will not be killed so soon as I thought he would. 

COUNTESS Why should he be killed? 

FOOL So say I, madam, if he run away, as I hear he	 does. The danger is in standing to ’t; that’s the loss of men, though it be the getting of children. Here they come will tell you more. For my part, I only hear your son was run away.	 

